content.rendered:
Directed by Aarun Nagar.

Written by Aarun Nagar.

Cast Aarun Nagar((Prathvi Singh)). Pramod Moutho((Kaka)). Shahbaaz Khan((Dharam Pal)). Sachin Khari((Beer Singh / Sher Singh) (as Sachin Gurjar)). Javed Rizvi((Titu) (as Javed Rizvi Jarehavi)). Garima Agarwal((Sarla Devi)). Anupama((Mohini)). Nandesh Gurjar(Veer Singh’s Friend). Ravi Verma((Jamalu)). Naushaad Abbas(Fighter (uncredited)) . Parveen Bansala((Kallu)). Mahaveer Singh Fauji((Mahaveer)). Anupama Prakash(Mohini). Khyati Sharma((Joolie-Item Girl)). Nishant Sharma(Boyfriend (credit only)). Ravi Sharma((Hariya))

Language Hindi.

Producer Priyanka Gurjar.

Production Kirti Motion Pictures. AJ Films Entertainment World. C.S.K Production.
